node.text:
It's always impossible to hide the comfort that the @cr7cristianoronaldo Underwear collection provides and the fun that we have every time we shoot a campaign. 
 
Especially behind the scenes. 😉 

#CR7UNDERWEAR

Proud to be partnering with @binance 🙏
 
Together we'll give you the opportunity to own an iconic piece of sports history.
 
I'm excited to take this journey with all of you. Let’s change the NFT game with #Binance.

I'm an Ambassador for upcoming football video game UFL, where my #CR7FansTeam will be present, and it is up to you to pick its lineup! Suggest your favorite players on UFL social media in 3 rounds between June 7 and June 28.

Simply follow the updates and comment your suggestions. See more details in @uflgame bio! 📝

Proud to be part of the Nike family and excited to celebrate their first 50 years. Throughout my entire career we have been on a journey together, a journey of progress. And we have achieved some amazing results. Think you’ve seen it all? Think again: we are never done!
@nike #teamnike #nike50

You need more than quick feet to be a champion. It takes hours of hard work, stubborn determination and a dose of fearlessness.
 #KeepAClearHead #beclearbefearless #bethefirstyou #clearxcr7

We’re opening a new Insparya clinic in Valencia! The 3rd in Spain and the 8th @insparya_es Group clinic.

The new clinic offers 1,600 m2, 12 premium hair transplant rooms, 4 treatment rooms and the most advanced technology in this area, developed by our R+D Insparya Science and Clinical Institute.

This new clinic is a major milestone for the group. Thank you to our amazing team and the 45,000 patients who trusted in @insparya_es .🙏🏽

#Valencia #NewOpening #ComingSoon #Insparya #ClinicaCapilar

Never let doubts or dandruff hold you back.

When the time comes, clear your head and unleash your fearless power.
#KeepAClearHead #BeClearBeFearless #BeTheFirstYou

Proud to overcome one more challenge by becoming the World’s Clubs Top Goal Scorer, only 6 months after becoming the World’s International Top Goal Scorer. Nothing but respect for Romário, one of the best strikers of all time! Thanks to all the players that I’ve come across throughout my career, thanks to all the clubs that I represented, thanks to all my fans, and above all, thanks to my wonderful family. I couldn’t have done it without you! 👏🏽🙏🏽

Marhaba! Thrilled to announce that I am now an official brand ambassador for @talabat , the leading food
and grocery delivery platform in the MENA region! Order your groceries and favorite meals from the
talabat app now, and make sure to watch the launch video… I had lots of fun filming this! #talabatMart
#TheGreatestDelivered #RonaldoXtalabat
𝟒𝟎𝟎… 𝐌𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐟𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐬 🙏🏽🙌🏽 #alwaystogether

Authentic and genuine, Cristiano Ronaldo Origins is a perfect fragrance for those of you who are passionate about life. 
Try it, Love it.

#CR7ORIGINS
Primeiros dois objectivos alcançados: apuramento e liderança no nosso grupo. Mas há ainda muito mais pela frente! Vamos Portugal! 🇵🇹❤️
O apuramento está garantido mas queremos também o 1.º lugar. Não há limites para esta equipa nem para os nossos objectivos. Vamos por mais! Força Portugal! 🇵🇹🙏🏽

Estamos nos oitavos do Mundial! Grande trabalho, equipa! Frente a um adversário de grande mérito, fizemos valer a nossa força e a nossa qualidade. Vamos em frente! Estamos na luta e o nosso sonho continua bem vivo! Força, Portugal! 💪🏽🇵🇹
Unidos e focados. Rumo ao nosso objectivo.🇵🇹🙏🏽

Marcar em 5 Campeonatos do Mundo é alcançar um feito que eu jamais ousaria sonhar, mas é também a prova de que não há impossíveis. O orgulho que sinto em representar Portugal só é comparável à alegria que sinto em cada golo que marco pelo meu país, traduzido em vitórias dedicadas ao nosso povo. Vamos em frente! Isto ainda está só a começar! 🇵🇹❤️
Vitória muito importante na nossa estreia neste Mundial, mas nada está ganho! Foi apenas o primeiro passo! Seguimos focados na busca dos nossos objectivos. Força Portugal!🇵🇹🙏🏽💪🏽

Prestes a iniciarmos a nossa campanha na maior competição do Mundo. Uma aventura que desejamos longa e repleta de sucessos, de forma a elevarmos bem alto o nome e a bandeira do nosso país. Queremos encher todos os portugueses de orgulho e alegria. Não há impossíveis! Força, Portugal! 🇵🇹🙏🏽💪🏽
Ever thought you’d see CR17, CR7, and CR Jr. together on the pitch?! ⚡⚽ #NikeFC
I’m excited to announce my partnership with @jacobandco , one of the leading watch brands in the world. Today, we reveal our first watch collection that I co-designed with my dear friend @jacobarabo

𝟓𝟎𝟎 𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐟𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐬! 🙌🏽
My life, career and thoughts,
shared with you, always.
You are part of my story
and together we´ve achieved so much.
More than I could dream.
In every post, each moment, your support.
Thank you! 🙏🏽
How many would you get right? Catch the full video in the watch section of the free @livescore app to see how I did.
